    <lb n="1"/>Πτολεμαῖος Διοδώρᾳ τῇ ἀδελφῇ 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>γινώσκειν</corr><sic>γινωσκιν</sic></choice> σε θέλω, ὅτι ὕπνος οὐ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κ</supplied> ἔρχε-

    <lb n="4"/>ταί μοι διὰ νυκτὸς <choice><corr>χάριν</corr><sic>χαρειν</sic></choice> τῆς σῆς 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>ἀπροαιρέσεως</corr><sic>σαπροεραισει</sic></choice> καὶ τῆς σῆς <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.183">ἀπρ<add place="supralinear">ο</add>θυμίας</lem><rdg>ἀπρο<gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/>ια?</rdg></app>, 

    <lb n="6"/>ἣν ποιεῖς μοι περὶ τῶν ἐμῶν. καὶ ἄν τι 

    <lb n="7"/>σπανίσω ἐκ τῶν ἐμῶν, σοῦ <choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">χά</supplied>ριν</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">χα</supplied>ρειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="8"/>γίνεται, ἤτ᾽ ἂν ἀναπλεύσω πρός <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied>ε καὶ 

    <lb n="9"/>μαρσίππιν <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.183"><seg cert="low" part="N"><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear></del></seg></lem><rdg>γ᾽</rdg></app> <choice><corr>εὕρω</corr><sic>ευρο</sic></choice> οὗ ζητῶ, ἤτ᾽ ἄν τι ἄλλο 

    <lb n="10"/>ὁμοίως. ἐκ σοῦ ἡδέως ἔχω παρ᾽ ἐμοὶ 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἀναπαύομαι</corr><sic>αναπαομαι</sic></choice> καὶ τῆς σῆς ἀπληστίας 

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἀδικίας</corr><sic>αδικειας</sic></choice>· πολεμεῖ με διότι εἶπόν σοι 

    <lb n="13"/>εἰς ὄψιν· <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.183"><choice><corr>οὐδὲν</corr><sic>ουτεν</sic></choice></lem><rdg>οὐ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied>ὲν</rdg></app> θέλω <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.183">παρὰ<choice><corr>σοῦ</corr><sic>σοι</sic></choice></lem><rdg>παρα<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">σχεῖν</supplied> σοι</rdg></app> <choice><corr>ἐφ᾽</corr><sic>επφ</sic></choice> ὅσον 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐν <choice><corr>Ἀλεξανδρίᾳ</corr><sic>αλεξανδριαν</sic></choice> εἰμί, εἰ μὴ μόνον τὸν 

    <lb n="15"/><choice><corr>ἱματισμὸν</corr><sic>ειματισμον</sic></choice> καὶ κεράμιν <choice><corr>ἐλαίου</corr><sic>αιλεου</sic></choice> κατ᾽ 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐνιαυτόν. ταῦτα ἐν ἐμαυτῷ <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.183">λέγων</lem><rdg><choice><corr>ἔλεγον</corr><sic>λεγον</sic></choice></rdg></app> ὡς 

    <lb n="17"/>πολλά σοι <choice><corr>ἐχαρισάμην</corr><sic>εχαρεισαμην</sic></choice> καὶ οὔτε αὐτὰ 

    <lb n="18"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="2" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="18"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="7.183">ἧκε <choice><corr>πεῖσαί</corr><sic>πισε</sic></choice></lem><rdg>ἧκ᾽ ἐπί σε</rdg></app> μοι τῷ λόγῳ, ἅμα καὶ 

    <lb n="19"/>γνώμην σοι λάβω περί <choice><corr>τινος</corr><sic>τινες</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>πράγμα<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">τος</supplied></corr><sic>πραγμα</sic></choice>, ἢ δι᾽ αὐτῶν <choice><corr>πέμψαι</corr><sic>πεμψε</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="21"/>ὃ θέλεις σὺν <choice><corr>ἐπιστολιδίῳ</corr><sic>επιστολιτιν</sic></choice>, ἐὰν 

    <lb n="22"/>μὴ θέλῃς σκυλῆναι οὕτως. 

    <lb n="23"/>ταῦτά σοι γράφω ὡς <choice><corr>ἀγνωμο-

    <lb n="24"/>νήσας</corr><sic>αγνομονησας</sic></choice> τῇ στάσει καὶ προσδοκῶ 

    <lb n="25"/>σοι. γεγύμνωμαι καὶ ὕβρισ-

    <lb n="26"/>μαι <sic>μαι</sic> παρὰ πάντων τῶν συνπο-

    <lb n="27"/>λιτῶν, καὶ δὸς Ταπασίτι <choice><corr>ὃ</corr><sic>το</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἔχεις</corr><sic>εχις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="28"/>αὐτὴν ἐν παραθέσει;  ἀσπάσο-

    <lb n="29"/>μαι Δῖον τὸν καὶ Κάστορα καὶ 

    <lb n="30"/>Πολυδεύκην καὶ Πεκῦσιν πολ-

    <lb n="31"/>λὰ καὶ Ἀφροδίτην καὶ <choice><corr>Ἑρμι-

    <lb n="32"/>όνη<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ν</supplied></corr><sic>ερμιονη</sic></choice> σὺν <choice><corr>τέκνοις</corr><sic>τεκνα</sic></choice> καὶ εἴ τις ἐμοὶ 

    <lb n="33"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἀ</unclear>σ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">π</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ι καὶ <gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>νι<gap reason="lost" extent="7" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="34"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.23086" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.23086" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low">ca. 200</date></p></div><div n="meta.23086" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">SB</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">4317</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">23086</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0239</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">4317</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0239;1;4317" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.23086" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Mélanges Chatelain, nach S. 282</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.23086" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="fr" default="NO"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">B. Haussoullier,</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="" default="NO"><head lang="de">in:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Mélanges Chatelain, S. 283-284</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.23086" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Alexandria</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>